@startuml VibeCodium - Sequence (Real-Time Collaboration)
title VibeCodium - Real-Time Collaboration

participant "User 1" as U1
participant "User 2" as U2
participant "Collaboration\nServer" as WS

U1 -> WS : Join project session
WS --> U1 : Sync current document state
note over U1,WS : User 1 is up to date

U2 -> WS : Join same project session
WS --> U2 : Sync current document state
note over U2,WS : User 2 is up to date

U1 -> WS : Edit — type "hello"
WS --> U2 : Broadcast change
note over U2 : Sees "hello" appear instantly

U2 -> WS : Edit — type " world"
WS --> U1 : Broadcast change
note over U1 : Sees "hello world"

U1 -> WS : Save file
WS --> U1 : Saved successfully

@enduml
